Package: libqoob0
Version: 0.13
Section: libs
Priority: optional
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, kmod
Maintainer: Joni Valtanen <jvaltane@kapsi.fi>
Description: library to operate with Nintendo Gamecube Qoob Pro mod-chip
 .
 libqoob is library to operate easily with Nintendo Gamecube Qoob Pro 
 mod chip. Library supports listing, writing, reading and erasing
 Qoob Pros flash. Reading supports only GCB file format. Writing
 supports GCB, DOL and ELF formats.
 
Package: libqoob-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Depends: libqoob0 (= ${source:Version}), libusb-dev, libc6-dev | libc-dev, ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: development files for libqoob
 .
 libqoob is library to operate easily with Nintendo Gamecube Qoob Pro 
 mod chip. Library supports listing, writing, reading and erasing
 Qoob Pros flash. Reading supports only GCB file format. Writing
 supports GCB, DOL and ELF formats.
 .
 This package contains header files and libraries needed to 
 compile applications that use libqoob.
